Usage: 
test env mode config: bash escommander.sh -m production -t 
clear previous indexes info with backup: bash escommander.sh -m production -a clear 
start with instances: sudo bash escommander.sh -m production -a start -n 2
remove instances: sudo bash escommander.sh -m production -a stop_instances


